import React from "react" import Exercise from "./Exercise" import NavBar from "./NavBar" function HomePage() { const handleExerciseButtonClick = (exerciseType) => { // Make a network request to the backend with exerciseType axios .get(`http://localhost:5000/api/questions-and-variables?exerciseType=${exerciseType}`) .then((response) => { // Handle the response from the backend // You can update the state or navigate to the CodingScreen component // with the fetched data based on the exerciseType console.log(response.data); // Check the response data in the browser console }) .catch((error) => { console.error("Error fetching data from the server:", error); }); }; return (
) } export default HomePage
